'''Dusk''' was a slow, dark and moody genre of [[Music/Legends|music]] common in the [[Mid Rim/Legends|Mid]] and [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories]] during the [[Time/Legends|time]] of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].
One dusk band was called [[Far Cry]].

